title: The Cigar Authority 3 Year Anniversary

description: It's Official! The Friggin' Catalina Wine Mixer! It's our 3rd Anniversary! Can you believe it? Special show for you.... We have the National Launch of a NEW Cigar and NEW Lighter from Brothers of the Leaf. Plus, the return of the Flowbee? Being used LIVE on the air? On Dave?! Light em up, and enjoy!
